    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep shine and absolutely no scratches, dents, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, featuring pristine upholstery and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, offering a smooth, powerful drive with a complete and up-to-date service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in climate-controlled storage and maintained to the highest possible standards.",
